Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美容师游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:38.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真喜欢玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  唯是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔跤了吗  一如既往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了不让吉太被淋湿才变成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裹上塑料袋不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得对啊  小澪真聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  一般都会想到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发虽然已经擦干了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  变得好蓬乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好不容易才梳好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅雨季节很潮湿  所以相当麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早上头发也是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一到梅雨季节就每天早上在镜子前奋斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  也是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以刚才很在意头发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是卷毛同志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同是卷毛  但这差距算什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  不把衣服弄干会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晾在活动室里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  让你们陪着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  室内鞋也都湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧身裤也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄来了热水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  一大早就喝茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:05:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用水桶来喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  是用来热脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就失礼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服至极  舒服至极
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已经不想上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  被训斥了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  觉得暖和了之后就把衣服脱下来  要晾干的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了  快点换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  我们已经把衣服挂起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吉太看到这个样子很难为情～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:06:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被敷衍了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  你要换什么衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天没有体育课  所以没带运动服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有小佐和亲手制作的衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部的负面遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你选这件！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你把这个藏在哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明应该还给小佐和了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把这个留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  唯  果然在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  班会要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会知道她是唯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？凭感觉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊  和和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能换的衣服只有这件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也有别的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要点名了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平泽同学  你这是什么打扮？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校服湿了  所以我就换上了这件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是  在学校里打扮成这种奇怪的样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这衣服明明是小佐和做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没别的衣服了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来迟了  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从其他班级的同学那里借来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的机会  想穿别的衣服看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了  快换掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓  找到忘拿的东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是姐姐的紧身裤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把这些东西晾在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不出口…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折缝烫不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:08:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真熟练啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纽扣差点就要掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你帮我缝好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不擅长这种精细活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缝钮扣倒是很快啊  律
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪费了  不想穿～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要坐下来就不会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问的是作为一个女生这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律不也经常这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动服要脱掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田井中同学也把下襟塞进去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前明明都不会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  平泽同学  田井中同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也很不轻松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  您不用为我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有为你担心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平泽同学也快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明这样比较好的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使裙子掀起来也没事  摔跤了也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了  快点脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和  住手～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:32.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  被摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等  就像我在袭击你似的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平泽同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:34.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是校服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点无聊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明大家都很期待的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用回应大家的期待也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  还在下雨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要被淋湿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:53.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天好像也会下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:54.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去也要保护好吉太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:10:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  早上还出了那种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我用了吉他的防水外套
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  还有那种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在网上买的  还是很方便的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原价3000日元却只要1980
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还送吉他用干燥剂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个也是在网上买的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  可以粘在墙上的吉他挂钩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉垫的形状哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这是让手指张得更开的强化道具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有别的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如在睡觉的时候培养节奏感的CD
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…这些全都有用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我终于知道在活动室晾衣服是怎么回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为纯她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这说不定是什么咒术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨着谁  就对其下了诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你看  特地跑到音乐室来晾衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…讲了那些话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧没好意思说吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  真是让人刮目相看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然挺身去保护吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎嘿嘿  再夸几句～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  要是不小心让吉他见了水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指板上很容易发霉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开盒子就看到上面全是霉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道吉太已经面目全非…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没发霉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但琴弦有些生锈了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是该换弦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次是什么时候换的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个月前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还是换一下好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.49,0:12:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有新弦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然敢攻击我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  请松开弦扭再剪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太  我现在就给你换新弦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱惜它是好事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也不用成天这么开心地跟它讲话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵你吃醋啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三角关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连律学姐也！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Triangle Love
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种苦恼的歌词也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连澪学姐也这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点告诉我就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦终于换好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就燃尽了可怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  赶紧练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨也停了  感觉也好起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！趁现在赶紧回家吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不练习了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太会淋湿的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又满嘴吉太吉太的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵对我也是很重要的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜  湿乎乎的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前天姐姐吃剩下的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发霉了…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶泡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐发霉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道吃了那个馒头？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  没啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你嘴边上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青海苔还沾着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  中午吃过章鱼丸子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅雨什么时候是个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨也不错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:15:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一整天都可以这样悠闲地在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始练吉他后  姐姐就一直都很满足
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是会担心能不能弹好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是太差劲的话  就觉得太对不起吉太了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但又说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能一直这么快乐地在一起就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:38.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（日本童谣「下雨歌」　北原白秋 作词　中山晋平 作曲）
