Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:04.87,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あめあめ　ふれふれ　かあさんが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:11.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,じゃのめで　おむかえ　うれしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:18.34,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ピッチピッチ　チャップチャップ　ランランラン
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也下雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天没问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这下放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太难拆了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包过头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于拆完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的气候对乐器比较苛刻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴颈受潮的话会弯曲导致走音的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试下八度调音就能听出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着  像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我也试试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏了半音的一半的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（半音：十二平均律相邻的两个音之间最小的距离叫半音，两个半音距离构成一个全音）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用调谐器就能听出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  和唯学姐说得一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏了1/8音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我调好吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去调啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的话太花时间啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:31.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我不是都教过你了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下不为例哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨还是不见停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风也越刮越大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气预报说明天还要继续下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就把贝司放在活动室好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了！小澪！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怜了  伊丽莎白！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要被抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想淋湿才放在这里的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有别随便起名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不唯你的吉他也放活动室吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包装用的塑料纸…都成那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跟不认识的人走掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽莎白  今晚要和吉太一起过夜哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不要随便起名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp30}　{\fsp1}Bass{\fsp140}　{\fsp1}Elizabeth{\r}\N因为是贝司所以起名叫伊丽莎白么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp100}　{\fsp1}Mustang{\r}\N那么  我的叫野马…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…穆炭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好配的名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要随便猜人家在想什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓你已经说出口了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔哇  这雨下得超大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋子里都进水了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:18:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好把乐器放学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太  好担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不带吉他到头来还是会淋湿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说唯也很重视她的吉他嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重视的方向错了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就放一天而已  太夸张啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  说那样的话好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次碰坏贝司的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭着跑来找我的事情你都不记得啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.97,0:19:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪儿呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业终于做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…小偷？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！我听到奇怪的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你没事吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.30,0:20:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心留在学校的吉太  睡不着觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来  买回吉他后天天都在练习
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都和吉太在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了了！我去取回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！这里是三层！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:21:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面下着雨！你还穿着睡衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一天没碰而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你笑得嘴都歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你很重视这把吉他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过班会的时候能不能收起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.09,0:21:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很在意！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～就一下下  没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.86,0:21:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯她那个样子  害得我都担心起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开盒子就看到上面全是霉～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽莎白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.20,0:23:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕  好可怕  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.71,0:23:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪搔痒耙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别弄出奇怪的东西来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.99,0:23:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是两人的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.12,0:23:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那之后等待着她们的命运…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.30,0:23:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就开始第一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止听到过的最可怕的事是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:23:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你在问什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.73,0:23:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.81,0:24:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二可怕的事是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.85,0:24:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个下一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.79,0:24:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三可怕的事是什么～？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.07,0:24:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…我明明已经要忘记那件事了…


